data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Price change! Also, sellers have agreed to contribute the amount necessary for a 2-1 interest rate buydown with the lender that saves $400/month on first year payments. Are you looking for a home that offers privacy, NO HOA, fully fenced and gated on 1.3 acres?  Then look no further! This beautiful, well-maintained home with newly updated kitchen, will not disappoint! The home sits in the middle of the property, so you have a nice big front yard and equally large back yard. As you walk up to the home, you are greeted by a covered front porch which is perfect for enjoying a nice restful afternoon of reading or just relaxing in a warm, Florida breeze. When you enter the home, you will find yourself in the spacious, living room with large windows to allow natural light, NEW LUXURY VINYL PLANK FLOORING, a ceiling fan and a floor plan that is open to the dining area and kitchen which lends itself to great entertaining space for family and friends. The recently renovated kitchen has new stainless-steel appliances, laminate flooring, granite countertops, a beautiful center island with granite countertop as well and ample storage on both sides. With so much cabinet and counter space, any chef would be happy to create their culinary masterpieces here. The home also offers a desirable split bedroom plan. The master suite is located at one end of the home and is large enough for a king size bed and all the accompanying furniture, has a ceiling fan, NEW VINYL PLANK FLOORING, and ensuite master bathroom with dual vanity, a large step-in shower with beautiful tile work, a big linen closet and his and hers walk-in closets. Bedrooms two and three are located on the other side of the home. Both have walk-in closets and are large enough to accommodate queen sized beds. The guest bath with tub/shower combo is conveniently located nearby. The large laundry room is located just off the kitchen with washer/dryer and utility sink. If the house itself didn't wow you enough, just step outside and see the 24x32 two car garage with ample space for two vehicles and plenty of room for all your tools and workbenches. This backyard is great space for a nice garden, playground or a pool and comes complete with a barn and chicken coop. The Seller will leave some chickens if the Buyer would like to have their own fresh eggs every morning. The AC is new in 2023 and the Septic was pumped in 2020. So what are you waiting for! Schedule your appointment today, and don't let this one get away!
